[61.541675, "o", "\r\n"]
[61.5422, "o", "  Three evaluations uploaded. Each hospital got a\r\n"]
[61.542244, "o", "  cryptographic receipt — proof their data was included.\r\n"]
[61.542257, "o", "  The server committed each value, added it to a Merkle tree,\r\n  updated running sums, and DISCARDED the individual values.\r\n  It can never recover them.\r\n"]
[67.550156, "o", "\r\n"]
[67.551183, "o", "  Next, hospitals share attack technique observations.\r\n"]
