[110.261381, "o", "\r\n"]
[110.858994, "o", "  \r\n    Analysis Report\r\n    ==================================================\r\n    Status: analyzed\r\n    Contribution ID: 835ccbf8-d36d-45...\r\n    Receipt: 9e26992120607938c5ed0d949d2d523f...\r\n    Merkle proof: 3 nodes\r\n    Dice chain: MISMATCH (local=1746168854960013... server=d9f727b77eab07b3...)\r\n    Campaign Match: Yes\r\n    Shared IOCs: 4\r\n    IOC Types: ip=1, email=1, hash-sha256=1, domain=1\r\n  \r\n    Actions (3):\r\n      [CRITICAL] Block matching network indicators at firewall and DNS\r\n             2 network IOCs (domains/IPs) match indicators seen across other organizations in the collective\r\n      [HIGH] Hunt for matching file hashes in your environment\r\n             1 file hash IOCs match the collective — search SIEM/EDR logs for the last 30 days\r\n      [HIGH] Hunt for related activity in your environment\r\n             Cross-reference the 4 matched IOCs with your SIEM/EDR logs for the last 30 days\r\n  \r\n"]
[113.891859, "o", "\r\n"]
[113.89255, "o", "  32 shared IOCs. Ohio isn't alone.\r\n  This is a coordinated campaign hitting multiple hospitals.\r\n"]
